text:
Bought the Bak Chor Mee, averagely good taste on the whole.

Texture of mee pok is slightly on the soft side. They also ofter mee kia, bee hoon, kway teow and mee tai mak.

Spiciness of the sambal chilli was averagely good, taste a bit of pork lard.

Bak Chor Mee includes 5 slices of fish cake, 2 fish balls and 1 pork minced ball at $4 ( price @2023)

Additional container is charged at 30 cents for take away. No additional charge for take away in plastic bag.
